original_title: El puto inolvidable: Vida de Carlos Jáuregui
overview: Carlos Jáuregui, gay rights activist, friend, lover, wrestler, icon, a mass inspiring. His conviction and pride changed the life of the Argentine LGBT Collective and the history of a country and its legislation.
tagline: Visibility for the LGBT movement wouldn’t have been the same without him.
title: Carlos Jáuregui: The Unforgettable Fag
